      <main class="px-3 mb-3 lh-5">
        <h1>What yelpcamp do ?</h1>
        <p class="lead fs-4"> YelpCamp is an interactive web platform designed for camping enthusiasts to explore, share, and review campgrounds. Users can create personalized accounts to manage their profiles and interact with a database of campsite listings. Each campground entry features detailed descriptions, photos, and user-generated reviews with ratings, fostering a community-driven approach to discovering ideal outdoor destinations. The platform incorporates interactive mapping functionalities, facilitated by technologies like MapTiler SDK, to visualize campground locations effectively. With a focus on user experience, YelpCamp also offers theme switching capabilities and employs Helmet.js for enhancing security by managing HTTP headers. Whether planning a trip or sharing experiences, YelpCamp provides a comprehensive hub for outdoor enthusiasts to connect and explore the world of camping.</p>
 
      </main>
